11.26.24  1:09 am   11 months ago i decided to commit to a weekly schedule and release a short film every saturday for 1 year. it's been going well and i only have a few more to make. the thing is, ive been thinking about making another video after all the weekly films are done where i go into the behind the scenes and explain why i made each one, where i got the idea and what went into them, not necessarily explaining the actual meaning behind them but still getting into it a bit. i'm wary that i shouldn't do this because if i explain the art it will change the way the audience views it, which i don't want to happen. however i still want people to understand and relate to the creative process. what do you think ?
